rule-4-2-a.test_description: A building has one building segment and one zone with an HVAC system that provides heating and cooling. The zone minimum humidity schedules match between the baseline and proposed ruleset model descriptions.

standard.rule_description: Humidity Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.

rule-4-2-b.test_description: A building has one building segment and one zone with an HVAC system that provides heating and cooling. The zone minimum humidity schedules do not match between the baseline and proposed ruleset model descriptions.
rule-4-2-b.expected_raised_message_includes: There is a humidity schedule mismatch between the baseline and proposed. Fail unless Table G3.1 #4 baseline column exception #s 1 and/or 2 are applicable

standard.rule_description: Humidity Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.

rule-4-2-c.test_description: A building has one building segment and one zone with an HVAC system that provides heating and cooling. The zone minimum humidity schedules do not exist in the baseline or proposed ruleset model descriptions.

standard.rule_description: Humidity Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.

rule-4-2-d.test_description: A building has one building segment and one zone with an HVAC system that provides heating and cooling. The zone minimum humidity schedules exists in the baseline ruleset model description but not the proposed.
rule-4-2-d.expected_raised_message_includes: Fail because a humidity schedule is defined in the baseline but not in the proposed.

standard.rule_description: Humidity Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.

rule-4-2-e.test_description: A building has one building segment and one zone with an HVAC system that provides heating and cooling. The zone minimum humidity schedules exists in the proposed ruleset model description but not the baseline.
rule-4-2-e.expected_raised_message_includes: Fail because a humidity schedule is defined in the proposed but not in the baseline.

standard.rule_description: Humidity Control Setpoints shall be the same for proposed design and baseline building design.
